<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>BreakUs</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="TrainerPage.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="bootstrap-5.1.3-dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="navegacion">
            <ul>
                <li class="breakus"><b>BreakUs</b></li>
                <nav>
                    <li id="rutineBtn">Rutinas</li>
                    <li id="usersBtn">Atletas</li>
                    <li id="profileBtn">Cuenta
                        <ul class="ul">
                            <li class="anotherli" id="trainerBtn">Datos</li>
                            <li class="anotherli" id="close_trainer">Cerrar Sesion</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                </nav>
            </ul>
        </div>           
    </header>
    <div id="rutines">
    <input type="button" name="newRoutine" value="Agregar nueva rutina" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#miModal" class="btn">
        <table id="tbl">
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <th class="title_exercise" name="newExerciseTitle"></th>
                    <td class="colum_exercise" name="newExerciseColum"></td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
    </div>
    <div class="modal fade" id="miModal" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true" aria-labelledby="modalTitle" data-bs-backdrop="static">
        <div class="modal-dialog">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <div class="modal-header">
                    <h3 class="p-3">Agrega una nueva rutina para los atletas</h3>
                    <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <form action="/TrainerPage/newRoutine" method="post" class="container form-group">
                        <p id="p">Por ahora, el servicio de BreakUs le brinda la oportunidad al entrenador de agregar 10 ejercicios para una nueva rutina. M치s adelante se implementar치 la opci칩n de agregar rutinas de manera m치s personalizada</p>
                        <input name="new_user" type="text" placeholder="Usuario del atleta" class="form-control m-2">
                        <small>Nota: si desea enviar a todos los usuarios, escriba asterisco (*)</small>
                        <input name="exercise1" type="text" placeholder="Ejercicio 1" class="form-control m-2">
                        <input name="exercise2" type="text" placeholder="Ejercicio 2" class="form-control m-2">
                        <input name="exercise3" type="text" placeholder="Ejercicio 3" class="form-control m-2">
                        <input name="exercise4" type="text" placeholder="Ejercicio 4" class="form-control m-2">
                        <input name="exercise5" type="text" placeholder="Ejercicio 5" class="form-control m-2">
                        <input name="exercise6" type="text" placeholder="Ejercicio 6" class="form-control m-2">
                        <input name="exercise7" type="text" placeholder="Ejercicio 7" class="form-control m-2">
                        <input name="exercise8" type="text" placeholder="Ejercicio 8" class="form-control m-2">
                        <input name="exercise9" type="text" placeholder="Ejercicio 9" class="form-control m-2">
                        <input name="exercise10" type="text" placeholder="Ejercicio 10" class="form-control m-2">
                        <button class="btn">Agregar Rutina</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container" id="trainer">
        <table class="table table-hover">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <td><b>Nombre</b></td>
                    <td><b>Apellido</b></td>
                    <td><b>Usuario</b></td>
                    <td><b>Correo</b></td>            
                    <td><b>Hora y fecha de registro</b></td>
                    <td><b>Plan asignado</b></td>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>        
                <tr>
                    <td></td>
                    <td></td>
                    <td></td>
                    <td></td>
                    <td></td>
                    <td></td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
    </div>
</body>
<script src="logout_trainer.js"></script>
<script src="TrainerPage.js"></script>
<script src="bootstrap-5.1.3-dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</html>